  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Äkäs Cabins are on a bed and breakfast basis with the option to upgrade to have half board meals <span>in the nearby</span> Äkäs Hotel. Half board includes a buffet breakfast and a three-course dinner.  </p>
<p>Guests staying on half board over New Year's Eve will have a gala dinner included, with live music and dancing. </p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests arriving before Christmas, for a Christmas celebration meal with games and music. Please note that for guests staying on half-board, the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option <span>or if you’re staying over Christmas the Festive Feast will take place on Christmas day and replace your half-board dinner on this day.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
