  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Äkas Cabins</strong> are about 31m² and sleep up to three people, with twin beds and a single sofa bed. The semi detached log cabins are all open plan and have private entrances.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Fireplace (firewood included)</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Small kitchen area with fridge, microwave, toaster, 2 ring hob and coffee maker</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made up on arrival</li>
<li>Final clean included (bins to be emptied before check-out)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
